<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>干旱终于过去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老棕熊巴鲁已经教了毛克利很多森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利还跟狼们学到了很重要的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼爸爸教毛克利注意声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林里的每个声音都有意义。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要仔细听草的声音和猫头鹰唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫头鹰会告诉你什么时候有危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的狼兄弟们教毛克利如何观察其他动物的行为。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蝙蝠休息之前挠树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鱼饿了就会在水池里跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，树上的猴子们一整天都在观察毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看见他用树枝盖了一个窝棚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看见他用小石子盖了一个小屋子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在淤泥里踩来踩去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利其实是在玩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像所有他那么大的孩子一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，猴子们不知道他只是在玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，他们惊奇地盯着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子非常聪明，多才多艺。”一个猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”另一个猴子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他可以当我们的首领！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”另一只也说，“如果他是我们的首领，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林里的所有动物都会嫉妒我们的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们找个办法把他带到猴子城来吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个炎热的下午，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们看见毛克利在和巴希拉、巴鲁一起睡午觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们偷来那个人类孩子的机会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只猴子低声说，“我们走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群猴子扑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来毛克利知道的是，几只手抓住了他的腿和胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，两只力气最大的猴子抓住毛克利逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>树枝刮了他的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>紧接着，他听见了巴鲁的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>熊的叫声惊醒了整个森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们越过树梢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇啊！”毛克利觉得头晕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>树枝和叶子拍打着他的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们蹦蹦跳跳，大喊大叫，穿过了森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放我走！”毛克利大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在高高的树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利担心猴子们会把他扔下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他开始生气、思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴鲁和巴希拉会找我的。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，猴子们跑得太快了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的朋友们可能追不上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他怎样才能留下线索告诉朋友们他在哪儿呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朝下看也没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只让毛克利觉得头晕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，他朝上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在上面远远的蓝天上，他看见了老鹰——兰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰飞在森林上空找吃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰终于朝下看，看见了猴子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”他说，“那些猴子抓着什么东西吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他俯冲下去，想要看清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利当然知道森林里的所有语言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吹了一声很响的口哨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊？”兰很惊讶，他吹哨回应。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利？是你吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“兰！跟着我！”毛克利朝老鹰喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，告诉巴鲁和巴希拉我在哪儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉爬上树去追毛克利，但猴子们太快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，细树枝承受不住黑豹的体重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉滑了下去，脚指甲里全是树皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁跑得很笨拙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快啊，巴希拉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你那个速度连受伤的牛都追不上。”巴希拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“坐着别动，我们来做个计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁趴到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太糟糕了！”巴鲁边打滚边呻吟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别像豪猪一样蜷着身子。”巴希拉厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得想想怎么办。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是……”巴鲁咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，毛克利现在可能已经死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>